2. cs.RO (Robotics) - The paper specifically deals with task allocation for robots, which is a sub-domain of robotics. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes an algorithm for task allocation, which involves AI techniques such as submodularity and sampling. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the control and coordination of multiple robots for task allocation, which falls under the domain of systems and control. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a new algorithm for task allocation, which involves data structures and algorithms.
